  "body": "This Pull Request updates dependency [sinon](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon) from `v4.1.1` to `v4.1.2`\n\n\n### Commits\n\n<details>\n<summary>sinonjs/sinon</summary>\n\n#### 4.1.2\n-   [`109e7b7`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/109e7b70432440193633b94c4b7649d91bff1319) Add markdownlint to dependencies\n-   [`12567cf`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/12567cf81549b371f3a86e96577e836447e6afc7) Update docs/changelog.md and set new release id in docs/_config.yml\n-   [`2af9818`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/2af98181a239322e73d252b71a76dc077feb2cf2) 4.1.2\n-   [`164fd2e`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/164fd2ee836c5a8659ad86b39dd333608ecdd6b6) Update History.md and AUTHORS for new release\n-   [`8de60ac`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/8de60ac34f2b3bdd6f89d9f1c9cef1f5ff1bde4a) Update Lolex to include fix for #&#8203;872\n-   [`bcc6960`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/bcc69607455906faae516748a52580827ddfe4d6) Remove deprecated methods from documentation (#&#8203;1613)\n-   [`ec3f489`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/ec3f4893f9d6bff451b32058fb6266b60b01b130) Ignore coveralls module when checking for unused dependencies\n-   [`5693d38`](https://github.com/sinonjs/sinon/commit/5693d3816dfcdebcbb6db8cb76841e9cb9aba422) Prefer node 8 for single run tests in Travis CI\n\n</details>\n\n\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://renovateapp.com).",
